trans-unit.source: Represents the data of a property for a selected item and enables editing of this property with type-specific data.
trans-unit.target: Representa os dados de uma propriedade de um item selecionado e permite a edição dessa propriedade usando dados de um tipo específico.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: The parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> pai.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> class that serves as a subproperty of the specified <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> que serve como uma subpropriedade do <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: For host infrastructure derived classes.
trans-unit.target: Classes derivadas para a infraestrutura de host.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> to apply.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> a ser aplicado.

trans-unit.source: Stores whether the target property value matches a specified <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" />.
trans-unit.target: Armazena se o valor da propriedade de destino corresponde à <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> especificada.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the category in which this property resides.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome da categoria na qual essa propriedade reside.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the name of the category.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.String" /> que contém o nome da categoria.

trans-unit.source: Enables the host infrastructure to create a new host-specific <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Habilita a infraestrutura de host a criar uma nova instância <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> específica do host.

trans-unit.source: A new <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um novo objeto <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the description of the encapsulated property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a descrição da propriedade encapsulada.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the description.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém a descrição.

trans-unit.source: Gets the display name for the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome de exibição para <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the display name.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém o nome de exibição.

trans-unit.source: Declaration of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> event, which occurs when a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> is changed through a call to the <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.ApplyFilter(System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Declaração do evento <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> que ocorre quando um <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> é alterado por meio de uma chamada ao método <see cref="M:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.ApplyFilter(System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter)" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether a set of standard values is available for this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se um conjunto de valores padrão está disponível para este <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if a set of standard values is available; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se um conjunto de valores padrão estiver disponível; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> is custom-made.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> é feito sob medida.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the property entry is custom-made; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se a entrada de propriedade personalizados?; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" /> é somente leitura.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the property entry is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se a entrada de propriedade é somente leitura; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> matches the filter.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> corresponde ao filtro.

trans-unit.source: Sets the value to indicate that the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> matches the filter and fires the event handler method for the property change.
trans-unit.target: Define o valor para indicar que o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> corresponde ao filtro e dispara o método do manipulador de eventos para a alteração da propriedade.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the target object matches the filter; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o objeto de destino corresponde ao filtro; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The `PropertyContainer` listens to changes made to this property.
trans-unit.target: O `PropertyContainer` escuta as alterações feitas a essa propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.String" /> display or type name of a filter to match against the target object.
trans-unit.target: O nome de tipo ou exibição <see cref="T:System.String" /> de um filtro a combinar com relação ao objeto de destino.

trans-unit.source: Implementation of a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> method that determines whether the target display or type name matches the specified string containing the name of a filter.
trans-unit.target: Implementação de um método <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget" /> que determina se a exibição de destino ou o nome do tipo corresponde à cadeia de caracteres especificada que contém o nome de um filtro.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the target display or type name matches the specified string; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o nome do tipo ou exibição de destino corresponder à cadeia de caracteres especificada; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> to apply.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter" /> a ser aplicado.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.FilterApplied" /> event.
trans-unit.target: Aciona o evento <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.FilterApplied" />.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.PropertyChanged" /> event.
trans-unit.target: Aciona o evento <see cref="E:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry.PropertyChanged" />.

trans-unit.source: The EventArgs for this event.
trans-unit.target: Os EventArgs para esse evento.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> PropertyChanged event.
trans-unit.target: Gera o evento PropertyChanged <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" />.

trans-unit.source: The name of the property whose value has changed.
trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade cujo valor foi alterado.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> event when the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainer" /> hears that the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> has changed.
trans-unit.target: Gera o evento <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> quando o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyContainer" /> ouve que o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> foi alterado.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> in classes derived from a host infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> pai em classes derivadas de uma infraestrutura de host.

trans-unit.source: A parent <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.
trans-unit.target: Um pai <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.

trans-unit.source: This is used only for subproperties, so its value can be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Isso é usado apenas para subpropriedades, portanto, seu valor pode ser `null`.

trans-unit.source: Declaration of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> event, which occurs when a property value changes.
trans-unit.target: Declaração do evento <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged" /> que ocorre quando um valor da propriedade muda.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome da propriedade.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the property name.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém o nome da propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém tipo da propriedade.

trans-unit.source: A type that contains the type of the property.
trans-unit.target: Um tipo que contém o tipo da propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> for this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> para este <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor" /> that is used for editing the value of this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor" /> que é usado para editar o valor deste <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor" /> object that contains the current editor.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValueEditor" /> objeto que contém o editor atual.

trans-unit.source: Gets a set of possible values supported by this <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um conjunto de valores possíveis compatíveis com este <see cref="T:System.Activities.Design.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> of possible values.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> de valores possíveis.
